summary: Complete FDO end-to-end protocol testing with TLS enabled
description: |
    Comprehensive FDO testing with TLS/HTTPS transport covering:
    - TLS certificate generation for HTTPS transport
    - Certificate infrastructure setup
    - Multi-server orchestration with TLS (manufacturer, rendezvous, owner)
    - Device initialization and onboarding over HTTPS
    - ServiceInfo module testing
    - Protocol validation with TLS

test: ../../rpm/test-onboarding-https.sh

framework: shell

duration: 30m

require:
  - go-fdo-server
  - go-fdo-server-manufacturer
  - go-fdo-server-owner
  - go-fdo-server-rendezvous

tag:
  - fdo
  - e2e
  - protocol
  - onboarding
  - tls
  - https
  - rpm
  - server

